import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; import { IMp3 } from '../mp-3.model'; @Component({ selector: 'jhi-mp-3-detail', templateUrl: './mp-3-detail.component.html', }) export class Mp3DetailComponent implements OnInit { mp3: IMp3 | null = null; constructor(protected activatedRoute: ActivatedRoute) {} ngOnInit(): void { this.activatedRoute.data.subscribe(({ mp3 }) => { this.mp3 = mp3; }); } previousState(): void { window.history.back(); } }
